CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 5, 1958, pg. 15, reads: "OES Recital - Omega Vesper Choir of Omega Grand Chapter, OES, presented Mrs. Mollie Johnson Lewis, second from left, in a recent recital at John Wesley AME Zion Church. Others in picture are, left to right, Mrs. Esther Green, Worthy Grand Matron; Mrs. Louise Kellum, Grand Organist, and Mrs. Edmonia Stevens, Grand Directness. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Esther Green, Mollie Johnson Lewis, Louise Kellum, and Edmonia Stevens, posed with large arrangement of chrysanthemums, in John Wesley AME Zion Church
